  "title": "アングラ演劇四天王",
  "created": 1777215830,
  "updated": 1777328504,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ee2953ee2782ee0be9257c",
      "text": "アングラ演劇四天王",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777215830,
      "updated": 1777215830
    },
    {
      "id": "69efdc410000000000b99925",
      "text": "既存の枠組みにとらわれない表現手法、ストリートや公園でのゲリラ的な公演。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777327169,
      "updated": 1777327170
    },
    {
      "id": "69efdc420000000000b99926",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777327171,
      "updated": 1777327171
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe0ed0000000000b99927",
      "text": "　[寺山修司]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777328365,
      "updated": 1777328376
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe0f80000000000b9992c",
      "text": "　 劇団「[天井桟敷]」を主宰し、言葉の魔術師とも呼ばれた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777328376,
      "updated": 1777328504
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe0ee0000000000b99928",
      "text": " [唐十郎]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777328367,
      "updated": 1777328386
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe1010000000000b9992d",
      "text": "  劇団「状況劇場（後の唐組）」を旗揚げし、紅テントでの活動が有名。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777328386,
      "updated": 1777328389
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe0ee0000000000b99929",
      "text": " [佐藤信]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777328367,
      "updated": 1777328401
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe1110000000000b9992e",
      "text": "  アンダーグラウンドシアター「自由劇場」などで活動した。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777328401,
      "updated": 1777328405
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe0ee0000000000b9992a",
      "text": " [鈴木忠志]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777328367,
      "updated": 1777328418
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe11a0000000000b9992f",
      "text": "  早稲田小劇場を拠点に独自の演劇理論を展開した。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777328411,
      "updated": 1777328414
    },
    {
      "id": "69efe0ef0000000000b9992b",
